\c 10
\p
\v 1 Zvino Samueri wakatora chinu chemafuta, ndokudurura pamusoro wake\x + 9.16. 16.13. 2 Sam. 2.4. 5.3. 1 Madz. 1.39.19.16. 2 Madz. 9.1,3,6. 11.12.\x*, ndokumutsvoda\x + Gen.. 41.40.\x*, ndokuti: Hakusi nekuda kwekuti Jehovha wakakuzodza kuti uve mutungamiriri pamusoro penhaka yake here\x + Det. 32.9. Map. 78.71.\x*?
\v 2 Kana wabva pandiri nhasi, zvino uchawana varume vaviri paguva raRakeri, pamuganhu waBhenjamini paZeriza\x + Gen.. 35.19,20.\x*; zvino vachati kwauri: Mbongoro hadzi dzawakaenda kunotsvaka dzawanikwa; zvino tarira, baba vako vasiya nyaya dzembongoro hadzi, asi votya pamusoro penyu\x + 9.5.\x*, vachiti: Ndichaita sei nekuda kwemwanakomana wangu?
\v 3 Kana wapfuurira mberi kubvapo, uchasvikawo pamuouki weTabhori\x + Gen.. 13.18.\x*, varume vatatu vagosanganapo newe vanokwira kuna Mwari kuBheteri\x + Vato. 20.31.\x*; umwe akatakura mbudzana nhatu, uye umwe akatakura mapundu matatu echingwa, uye umwe akatakura dende rewaini.
\v 4 Zvino vachakubvunza upenyu, ndokukupa zvingwa zviviri, zvauchagamuchira paruoko rwavo.
\v 5 Shure kweizvozvo uchasvika pachikomo chaMwari\x + 10.10.\x*, pane boka revarwi reVaFirisitia\x + 13.3,4. 2 Sam. 8.6,14. 1 Makor. 11.16. 18.13. 2 Makor. 17.2.\x*. Zvino zvichaitika pauchasvikapo paguta, kuti uchasangana neboka revaporofita vachiburuka kubva kunzvimbo yakakwirira, uye mberi kwavo kune mutengeranwa\x + 9.12.\x*, nengoma, nenyere\x + Gen.. 31.27. 2 Madz. 3.15. Eki. 15.20.\x*, nembira, vachiporofita\x + Gen.. 31.27. 2 Madz. 3.15. Eki. 15.20.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino Mweya waJehovha achauya nesimba pamusoro pako\x + 10.10. 11.6. 16.13. Vato. 14.6,19. Vato. 3.10. Num.. 11.25.\x*, ugoporofita pamwe navo, uye uchashanduka kuva umwe munhu\x + 10.10. 19.23,24.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino kuchati zviratidzo izvi pazvinokusvikira, iwe ita ruoko rwako zvarwuchawana\x + Eki. 4.8. Vato. 6.17. Ruk. 2.12.\x*, nokuti Mwari anewe\x + Josh. 1.5.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino uchaburuka mberi kwangu uende kuGirigari\x + 11.14,15. 13.4. Josh. 5.9.\x*; zvino tarira, ndichaburukira kwauri kuti ndipe zvipo zvinopiswa, ndibaye chibairo chezvipo zvekuyananisa; ucharinda mazuva manomwe kusvika ndasvika kwauri ndigokuudza zvauchaita\x + 13.8.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino kwakati paakafuratira kuti abve kuna Samueri, Mwari wakamupa umwe moyo; zvino zviratidzo izvi zvose zvikauya nemusi uyo.
\v 10 Pavakasvikapo pachikomo\x + 10.5.\x*, tarira, boka revaporofita rakamuchingamidza\x + 19.20.\x*; Mweya waMwari ndokuuya nesimba pamusoro pake; zvino wakaporofita pakati pavo\x + 10.6.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino zvakaitika, vose vaimuziva zuro \add na\add*marimwezuro pavakaona kuti, tarira, anoporofita pamwe nevaporofita, vanhu vakati umwe kune umwe: Chii ichi chawira mwanakomana waKishi? Ko Saurowo uri pakati pevaporofita\x + 19.24. Mat. 13.54,55.\x*?
\v 12 Zvino umwe wepo wakapindura, ndokuti: Asi ndiani baba vavo\x + Isa. 54.13.\x*? Naizvozvo yakava tsumo \add kuti\add*: Ko Saurowo uri pakati pevaporofita\x + 19.24. Mat. 13.54,55.\x*?
\v 13 Zvino apedza kuporofita wakasvika panzvimbo yakakwirira.
\p
\v 14 Zvino babamunini vaSauro vakati kwaari nekumuranda wake: Maiva maendepi? Iye ndokuti: Kunotsvaka mbongoro hadzi; zvino taona kuti hadziko, takasvika kuna Samueri\x + 14.50.\x*.
\v 15 Babamunini vaSauro ndokuti: Ndiudze hako Samueri zvaakataura kwamuri.
\v 16 Sauro ndokuti kuna babamunini vake: Wakatiudza pachena kuti mbongoro hadzi dzawanikwa. Asi nyaya yeumambo Samueri yaakataura, haana kumuudza\x + 9.20.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Samueri wakadanira vanhu pamwe kuna Jehovha\x + 11.15.\x* paMizipa\x + 7.5,6. Josh. 18.26.\x*.
\v 18 Ndokuti kuvana vaIsraeri: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri: Ini ndakakwidza Israeri kubva paEgipita, ndikakununurai kubva muruoko rweVaEgipita, neparuoko rweumambo hwose hwaikumanikidzai\x + 12.8. Vato. 6.8,9.\x*.
\v 19 Asi nhasi imwi maramba Mwari wenyu, iye amene anokuponesai panjodzi dzenyu dzose nenhamo dzenyu, uye mati kwaari: Kwete, isai mambo pamusoro pedu\x + 8.7,19. 12.12.\x*. Zvino ikozvino, zvimisei pamberi paJehovha nemarudzi enyu uye nezvuru zvenyu\x + Josh. 24.1.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino Samueri wakaswededza marudzi ose aIsraeri, rudzi rwaBhenjamini ndokubatwa\x + Josh. 7.14,16,17. Vato. 20.9.\x*.
\v 21 Akaswededza rudzi rwaBhenjamini nemhuri dzavo, mhuri yaMatiri ndokubatwa; zvino Sauro mwanakomana waKishi wakabatwa. Vakati vachimutsvaka haana kuwanikwa.
\v 22 Naizvozvo vakabvunzazve kuna Jehovha kuti munhu uyu achazosvika pano here? Jehovha ndokuti: Tarirai, wakavanda panhumbi\x + 23.2,4,9,10,11.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino vakamhanya ndokumutorapo; wakati azvimisa pakati pevanhu, waiva akareba kupfuura vanhu vose kubva pafudzi rake zvichikwira\x + 9.2.\x*.
\v 24 Samueri ndokuti kuvanhu vose: Munomuona iye Jehovha waakasarudza, kuti hakuna wakaita saiye pakati pevanhu vose here? Vanhu vose ndokudanidzira ndokuti: Mambo ngaararame\x + 2 Sam. 21.6.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino Samueri wakaudza vanhu nzira yeumambo, ndokunyora mubhuku, ndokuisa pamberi paJehovha. Samueri ndokuendesa vanhu vose, umwe neumwe kumba kwake\x + 8.11. Det. 17.14-20.\x*.
\p
\v 26 NaSaurowo wakaenda kumba kwake kuGibhiya\x + 11.4. Josh. 18.28.\x*; uye kwakaenda pamwe naye mhare dzemoyo yavo Jehovha yaaiva abata.
\v 27 Asi\x + 11.12.\x* vana vaBheriari vakati: Uyu angatiponesa sei\x + Det. 13.13.\x*? Zvino vakamushora, uye havana kumuvigira chipo. Asi wakazvinyararira\x + 16.20. 17.18. 25.27.Gen.. 43.11. Vato. 3.15. 2 Sam. 8.2,6. 1 Madz. 4.21. 10.25. 2 Makor. 17.5. Map. 72.10. Mat. 2.11. Zvir. 18.16.\x*.